{
  "texts": [
    "This information could be used to develop model design prompts and perform LLM-based model construction for de novo models.With this in mind, there are numerous potential applications for LLM-based model construction.",
    "As a first use case, AI-generated models could be used to rapidly perform double-programming technical validation of human-built models.",
    "This is a method in which the same model is built independently by two health economists, and differences in the results are investigated to reveal technical errors.",
    "In this use case, the LLM could take on the role of one of the two health economists to save time and potentially increase accuracy.",
    "Secondly, LLM-based model construction could enable rapid production of additional models to perform assessments of structural uncertainty."
  ]
}